README.md
     1вҶ’# Tock
     5вҶ’[Features](#features) вҖў [Quick Start](#quick-start) вҖў [Commands](#commands) вҖў
     6вҶ’[Configuration](#configuration) вҖў [Theme](#theme) вҖў [File Format](#file-format) вҖў [Shell](#shell-completion) вҖў [Inspiration](#inspiration) вҖў [License](#license)
     7вҶ’
     8вҶ’## Features
    12вҶ’**Tock** is a powerful time tracking tool for the command line. It saves activity logs as plaintext files and provides an interactive terminal UI for viewing your time.
    13вҶ’
    14вҶ’Features include:
    15вҶ’
    16вҶ’- рҹ“қ **Simple plaintext format** - Activities stored in human-readable files
    17вҶ’- рҹ“… **Notes & Tags** - Attach detailed notes and tags to activities
    18вҶ’- рҹҺЁ **Interactive TUI** - Beautiful terminal calendar view using Bubble Tea
    19вҶ’- вҡЎ **Fast & Lightweight** - Single binary, no dependencies
    20вҶ’- рҹ”„ **Compatible** - Reads/writes Bartib file format and TimeWarrior data files
    21вҶ’- рҹҺЁ **Customizable Themes** - Multiple color themes and custom color support
    22вҶ’- рҹ“… **iCal Export** - Generate .ics files for calendar integration, or sync with system calendars (macOS only)
    23вҶ’
    24вҶ’<hr clear="right"/>
    25вҶ’
