   116вҶ’## Configuration
   118вҶ’Tock supports a flexible configuration system using YAML files and environment variables.
   119вҶ’
   120вҶ’**Priority Order:**
   121вҶ’
   122вҶ’1. Command-line flags
   123вҶ’2. Environment variables
   124вҶ’3. Configuration file (`~/.config/tock/tock.yaml` or `./tock.yaml`)
   125вҶ’4. Default values
   126вҶ’
   127вҶ’### Configuration File
   165вҶ’### Environment Variables
   179вҶ’### Storage Backends
   183вҶ’### 1. Flat File (Default)
   191вҶ’### 2. TimeWarrior
   209вҶ’### Calendar View
   238вҶ’## Theming
   240вҶ’Tock supports customizable color themes for the calendar view.
   241вҶ’
   242вҶ’You can configure the theme in `tock.yaml`:
   243вҶ’
   244вҶ’```yaml
   245вҶ’theme:
   246вҶ’  name: custom
   247вҶ’  primary: "#ff0000"
   248вҶ’```
   249вҶ’
   250вҶ’Or use environment variables:
   251вҶ’
   252вҶ’### Theme Name
   262вҶ’### Auto-detection
   270вҶ’### Custom Colors
   283вҶ’### Example: Cyberpunk / Fuchsia Theme
   300вҶ’### Time Format
   316вҶ’#### 12-Hour Format Examples
   328вҶ’#### 24-Hour Format (Default)
   343вҶ’## Commands
   345вҶ’```bash
   346вҶ’
   347вҶ’A simple timetracker for the command line
   348вҶ’
   349вҶ’Usage:
   350вҶ’  tock [command]
   351вҶ’
   352вҶ’Available Commands:
   353вҶ’  add         Add a completed activity
   354вҶ’  analyze     Analyze your productivity patterns
   355вҶ’  calendar    Show interactive calendar view
   356вҶ’  completion  Generate the autocompletion script for the specified shell
   357вҶ’  continue    Continues a previous activity
   358вҶ’  current     Lists all currently running activities
   359вҶ’  help        Help about any command
   360вҶ’  ical        Generate iCal (.ics) file for a specific task, all tasks in a day, or all tasks
   361вҶ’  last        List recent unique activities
   362вҶ’  list        List activities (Calendar View)
   363вҶ’  remove      Remove an activity
   364вҶ’  report      Generate time tracking report
   365вҶ’  start       Start a new activity
   366вҶ’  stop        Stop the current activity
   367вҶ’  version     Print the version info
   368вҶ’  watch       Display a full-screen stopwatch for the current activity
   369вҶ’
   370вҶ’Flags:
   371вҶ’  -b, --backend string   Storage backend: 'file' (default) or 'timewarrior'
   372вҶ’      --config string    Config file directory (default is $HOME/.config/tock/tock.yaml)
   373вҶ’  -f, --file string      Path to the activity log file (or data directory for timewarrior)
   374вҶ’  -h, --help             help for tock
   375вҶ’  -v, --version          version for tock
   376вҶ’Use "tock [command] --help" for more information about a command.
   377вҶ’```
   378вҶ’
   379вҶ’[**вҶ’ Commands Reference**](docs/commands.md)
